    <description>South Africa's War is a supplement to the Panzer Grenadier series, focusing on the actions of these units during 1941. This module is not playable by itself, but requires ownership of Panzer Grenadier: Desert Rats to play all of the scenarios, and Panzer Grenadier: Afrika Korps, Panzer Grenadier: Eastern Front and  Panzer Grenadier: Road to Berlin to play some of them.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Contents include: Comb-bound, 22-page scenario booklet printed on cardstock. Includes special rules for South African troops and 20 new scenarios for the Panzer Grenadier game system. Also included is a sheet of 88 die-cut counters representing the infantry, weapons, vehicles and leaders of South Africa that were engaged in the fighting in North Africa.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This game is part of the Panzer Grenadier series&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
